Prepare Bob Evans Original Mashed Potatoes by following the recommended microwaving instructions on the package. Prepare Bob Evans Macaroni and Cheese by following the recommended microwaving instructions on the package. Place 2 oz. of Bob Evans Macaroni and Cheese in a martini glass. Sprinkle 1 Tbsp toasted bread crumbs over Macaroni and Cheese. Place 3 oz. of Original Mashed Potatoes in a martini glass. Sprinkle 2 Tbsp shredded cheddar cheese over mashed potatoes. Top with diced ham. Garnish with 1 tsp. chopped parsley.